asset.hookText:
World-class athletes, tech pioneers, health experts, and Nike Digital Sport leadership convened in New York City to introduce enhancements to the Nike+ ecosystem including the new Nike+ FuelBand SE.

Their message was clear. Move more, move more often and move with intensity.
